		<part part_index="1" name="World's first wizard school" page="0" source="2">
      	<article allWordsNum="92">
            	<![CDATA[
Look! The man wears a wizard costume and has a wand (魔杖). He dresses like Dumbledore, Harry Potter's headmaster. Do you know who he is? He is Oberon Zell Ravenheart. He opened the world's first wizard school in America.
In the magic school, there are 735 students. Like Hogwarts, students who attend the school are split into (分成) four different "houses (家族)" and like Harry Potter, they need to learn how to practise magic.
The school teaches 16 courses, including alchemy (炼金术), horse whispering (马语), wand making and spell casting (施咒语术). Oberon says his students are future Harry Potters.
          	]]>
            </article>
